{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You, malevolent King, have learnt the ways of Sorcery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather wilful servants by enslaving varied tribes \u2013</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect trinkets to enhance your fighters in unique ways \u2013</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321850/extras/sgbot.gif?t=1738430457\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">RTS-Roguelite Blend</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">HyperCoven plays like an RTS, but production of units is automatic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Capture different <strong>Coven</strong> which supply troopers for you to send into battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each trooper has up to 7 different attributes that can be enhanced with trinkets found in the world and buildings erected in base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Campaign</strong> spans 10 hand-crafted missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Conquest Mode</strong> is about venturing out to conquer the whole (randomized) world, as you would venture into a dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Invasion Mode</strong> is a take on the &quot;wave defense&quot; idea, the world is more sparse, but extra-dimensional invaders are warping in and drop valuable items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321850/extras/gate-mayy3.gif?t=1738430457\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiplayer </strong>is available for try-hard player versus player action, as well as co-op Conquest/Invasion runs.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3321850?t=1738430457","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3321850?t=1738430457","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321850/f032cd96fb0c4929ee7a9005723c3b4dbcbd935a/cap